---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Podcast — Don't Lose Your Way" description="Listen to stories, reflections, and voices from people who almost gave up — and stayed.">

  <section class="podcast-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Podcast</h1>
      <p class="podcast-subtitle">Stories from people who almost gave up — and stayed.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container podcast-body">
      <div class="podcast-intro">
        <p>Sometimes you need to hear a voice. Not advice. Not a lecture. Just someone who gets it.</p>
        <p>The Don't Lose Your Way podcast features anonymous stories, reflections, and conversations from people who've been in the quiet moments and found their way through.</p>
        <p>Coming soon.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="podcast-placeholder">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v7a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3Z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="19" y2="22"/></svg>
        <p>Episodes launching soon. Follow us to be notified.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="podcast-links">
        <p>Available on:</p>
        <div class="platforms">
          <span>Spotify</span>
          <span>Apple Podcasts</span>
          <span>YouTube</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .podcast-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .podcast-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .podcast-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .podcast-body {
    max-width: 40rem;
  }

  .podcast-intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .podcast-intro p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .podcast-placeholder {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .podcast-placeholder svg {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .podcast-placeholder p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .podcast-links {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .podcast-links p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .platforms {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .platforms span {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding: 0.375rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 9999px;
  }
</style>